{"slug":"the-legend-and-the-hero-ii","title":{"en":"The Legend and the Hero II","km":"គម្ពីតែងតាំងទេវតា វគ្គ២"},"description":{"en":"This sequel picks up where the first season left off, focusing on the great war between the Western Zhou and the Shang Dynasty. King Wu of Zhou, guided by the master strategist Jiang Ziya, leads a rebellion to overthrow the tyrannical King Zhou of Shang. The series features epic battles involving gods, demons, and magic, as the fox spirit Daji tries to protect her power against the rising army of divine generals.","km":"រឿងនេះគឺជាភាគបន្តពីវគ្គមុន ដែលផ្តោតសំខាន់ទៅលើសង្គ្រាមរវាងនគរ Zhou (ចូវ) និងនគរ Shang (សាង)។ ស្តេច Wu នៃនគរ Zhou ដោយមានការជួយជ្រោមជ្រែងពីលោកតា Jiang Ziya (ជាំង ជឺយ៉ា) បានដឹកនាំកងទ័ពបះបោរ ដើម្បីផ្ដួលរំលំស្តេច Zhou នៃនគរ Shang ដែលមានចិត្តឃោរឃៅ។ សាច់រឿងពោរពេញទៅដោយការប្រយុទ្ធគ្នាយ៉ាងខ្លាំងក្លារវាងទេវតា និងបិសាច រួមទាំងការប្រើប្រាស់មន្តអាគមផ្សេងៗ ខណៈដែលបិសាចកញ្ជ្រោង Daji (តាជី) ខិតខំការពារអំណាចរបស់ខ្លួនពីការវាយប្រហាររបស់កងទ័ពទេវតា។"},"poster":"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgPdLjisdTlmsAoOeEEoC8g7TaHtGHgzXOK1mSOydVj2IAdUAxegfw6HYUG3iAiOzanP0_62_eT33OL9JNG-QsdNTx37nLssOzDupDu4uHlwrVvGlM2HAhx67Xg-xWfU0-boXVVLohIcFv_U-DE-SxJ3XxfanGeH83EcXo9Su9-1WJOMqUcUxwWHNF0fgEE/s16000/unnamed.jpg","year":2009,"rating":7.2,"genres":["ACTION","COMEDY","DRAMA","HORROR","ROMANCE","THRILLER","FANTASY","DOCUMENTARY"],"language":"English","episodeCount":48,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/dm/refs/heads/bjt1/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/dm/refs/heads/bjt2/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"3","title":{"en":"Episode 3","km":"ភាគទី3"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/dm/refs/heads/bjt3/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"4","title":{"en":"Episode 4","km":"ភាគទី4"},"url":"https://raw.gi